================================================================================
IMPORTANT TRADING SYSTEM DISCLAIMER (NOT LEGAL ADVICE)
================================================================================

This repository contains algorithmic trading software for Nifty futures
on Indian exchanges via Zerodha Kite Connect.

1. This is experimental research software. It is NOT production trading
   infrastructure.
2. Trading futures and options involves substantial risk of loss and is not
   suitable for all investors. Past performance (backtest or paper) is not
   indicative of future results.
3. The authors and contributors accept ZERO liability for any financial loss,
   including but not limited to losses from bugs, incorrect assumptions,
   broker outages, regulatory changes, or misuse of this code.
4. Before using any part of this system with real capital (even micro size):
   - Perform your own independent validation over multiple market regimes.
   - Conduct extended paper trading with live data and real reconciliation.
   - Have the full system reviewed by a qualified compliance / risk professional.
   - Understand every line of code that can place or influence orders.
5. The "do not use real capital" warnings in the README are not boilerplate.
   They are the result of painful real-world experience with algo trading systems.

Use at your own extreme risk. Or better yet — don't, until you have the
statistical power and operational maturity to justify it.
